m;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">代码简洁易读，约 1200 行 Python 代码实现</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;line-height:1.5em;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">集成多种优化技术，包括前缀缓存、张量并行、Torch 编译和 CUDA 图等</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;line-height:1.5em;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">API 接口设计与 vLLM 类似，便于使用和迁移</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;margin-top:5px;line-height:1.5em;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">在 RTX 4070 硬件上对 Qwen3 模型进行基准测试表现出较高吞吐率和更快推理时间</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding-top: 0px;padding-bottom: 0px;padding-left: 10px;padding-right: 0px;display: block;color: rgb(0, 150, 136);margin-top: 0.2rem;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom: 0.2rem;margin-left: auto;border-left-width: 3px;border-left-style: solid;border-left-color: rgb(0, 150, 136);\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0em;display:block;font-size:22px;line-height:1.5em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">btjawa/BiliTools</span><span style=\"font-size: 0.58em;font-weight: normal;font-style: italic;color: graytext;display: block;text-decoration: underline;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://github.com/btjawa/BiliTools\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/btjawa/BiliTools</a></span></span></span></h2>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding-top:3px;letter-spacing:0em;padding-left:0px;font-size:16px;padding-bottom:3px;line-height:1.5em;margin-right:0px;margin-left:0px;text-indent:0em;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:justify;padding-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Stars:&nbsp;</span><code style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.2em;letter-spa